name: Popfrog
description: $POPFROG, a new community-driven memecoin on the Solana blockchain led by former $POPCAT whales. $POPFROG emphasizes community participation, entertainment, and meme-driven engagement, positioning itself as a complementary project within the broader ecosystem of Solana-based tokens. Complementing the token launch, an accessible browser-based game is now available on the project website. The game involves simple tap-to-jump mechanics integrated with Solana elements, with future updates planned to include on-chain leaderboards and token-based rewards to enhance user interaction.
